      "relations": null,
      "text": [
        " الْكَعْبِ إِذَا رُضَّ فَجُبِرَ عَلَى غَيْرِ عَثْمٍ وَ لَا عَيْبٍ ثُلُثُ دِيَةِ الرِّجْلِ ثَلَاثُمِائَةٍ وَ ثَلَاثَةٌ وَ ثَلَاثُونَ دِينَاراً وَ ثُلُثُ دِينَارٍ ."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.hubeali": [
          "And regarding the heel when it is bruised, so it is bandaged upon and there is no fault, is one-third of the wergild of the leg, being three hundred and thirty-three Dinars and one-third of a Dinar."
        ]
      }
    }
